{"tid":2016990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【南韓疫情】補習老師去梨泰院夜店後染疫　隱瞞病情令13名學生家長同事確診","createTime":"2020-05-14T22:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:50:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b32eb13f76a4961bf41e181dfb07a8d9a71ecf7","tid":2016990,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T22:29:46.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，南韓近日疫情出現反彈。一名29歲「梨泰院毒王」因去過5間夜店狂歡，而導致發生群聚感染事件，相關新冠肺炎確診個案已增加至120宗。當中，仁川一名補習老師去過夜店後確診，導致13名學生、家長、同事相繼確診。<br />\n<br />\n綜合韓媒報道，該名仁川數學補習老師為25歲，於5月2日、3日曾前往梨泰院夜店，曾與一名患者在梨泰院小食檔共坐一桌，並在9日確診。期間，他繼續去補習社上課及上門授課，沒有戴口罩，結果傳染了同補習社的1名同事、6名學生、1名學生家長，另外又傳染了上門授課的一對雙胞胎和家人。該對雙胞胎又傳染了另一名補習老師及與其接觸過的一人，前後共13人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該補習老師最初接受防疫部門調查時，宣稱自己「無業」，還隱瞞曾去夜店的行程，繼續授課，最終四處傳染病毒。防疫當局見他行蹤交代不清，便調查手機定位資訊，發現他在補習社當補習老師，更曾在夜店群組出現首名確診者當晚，不戴口罩地授課，才確認有其他接觸者，立即送往隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n另外，受感染的其中2名學生更被發現曾在確診前前往教會禮拜，2間教會當日分別有350人及700人參與，即有1050人曾和確診學生停留在同一密閉空間，將全數安排檢測。<br />\n<br />\n首爾市長朴元淳14日接受TBS電台訪問時表示，首爾梨泰院夜店群聚感染事件中，目前已進行了逾2萬個檢查，自導入匿名檢測制度後，受檢人數增加到平時的8倍，相關確診人數已達120人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2640000/2642955/itaewon_thumb_20200514_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2640000%2F2642955%2Fitaewon_thumb_20200514_S_1024.jpg&h=15f49968&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ba06d9569f22e6d14855f9f0525f2390203e5d4","tid":2016990,"uid":346806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T22:32:02.000Z","msg":"今次應該真無業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff96f5a608cc6bedfbd6b502bbc01c728d952dbe","tid":2016990,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T23:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7b0dbda3f1ea93dd2b016001eaa32f2ff8d38e","tid":2016990,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T23:20:53.000Z","msg":"香港都就快有叫雞群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364f66ece848cc8cd93bbc7478cd3b208d5b970b","tid":2016990,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad7b0dbda3f1ea93dd2b016001eaa32f2ff8d38e","tid":2016990,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T23:20:53.000Z","msg":"香港都就快有叫雞群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81eb12e6955dd35e41ecf2dc85e3ba1cfec4a89c","tid":2016990,"uid":45518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:13:46.000Z","msg":"防疫當局見他行蹤交代不清，便調查手機定位資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e45538f96804964fabec9bb52745abe2841c7ab","tid":2016990,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81eb12e6955dd35e41ecf2dc85e3ba1cfec4a89c","tid":2016990,"uid":45518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:13:46.000Z","msg":"防疫當局見他行蹤交代不清，便調查手機定位資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:17:48.000Z","msg":"人地國家用data黎做正義既事"},{"pid":"976dda9befec76008add3c0b1ae867f53e258813","tid":2016990,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ba06d9569f22e6d14855f9f0525f2390203e5d4","tid":2016990,"uid":346806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T22:32:02.000Z","msg":"今次應該真無業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:33:57.000Z","msg":"一語成讖<img src=\"/assets/